- Linux kernel 3.10-3 (3.10.11-1)<br />
- all packages have been updated from Debian testing repositories as of 2013/10/05<br />
- SparkyBackup-System one more bug fixed (thanks to The Black Pig) &#8211; updated up to 0.1.5<br />
