- added Teamviewer client, Sparky APTus, Minitube, Gnote, Osmo, Radiotray and Xfburn</p>
<p>New forum is also available for English speakers : <a href="http://sparkylinux.org/forum/" target="_blank">http://sparkylinux.org/forum/</a></p>
<p>Known bugs:<br />
- in some cases the live installer &#8220;can&#8217;t see&#8221; any disk (hard/usb) if an USB disk is plugged in
</p>
